-- XL Group Hires Export-Import Bank’s Abramson for Global Products
-- B y   M a r c i   J a c o b s
-- 2013-10-03T19:52:17Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-03/xl-group-hires-export-import-bank-s-abramson-for-global-products.html
XL Group Plc (XL) , the insurer led by
Chief Executive Officer Mike McGavick, hired Jeffrey Abramson as
senior vice president and global product leader as the company
expands into the supplier trade credit market.  Abramson, who joined from the Export-Import Bank of the
U.S., reports to Richard Maxwell, chief underwriting officer and
global head for XL Group’s political risk and trade credit
business, the Dublin-based insurer said today in a statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marci Jacobs in New York at 
